<br>
It works something like this:<br>
<br>
Your character has a list of every faction in the game, and next to that faction, there is a number.<br>
<br>
Every NPC in the game is effected by one or more factions. For example all the NPCs in the temple of solusek ro are on the &quot;temple of solusek ro&quot; faction.<br>
<br>
I believe when you faction is around 0(thats zero) then you con them at Indiffrent. When your number for that faction is in the negetives you will con Apprehensive, dubious, threateningly, and ready to attack, depending on how far below zero your faction is. This is just the opposite if you have positive faction Amiable, Kindly and Warmly if your faction is above 0(zero).<br>
<br>
Well, when you kill a shadowman, you get the messages &quot;your faction with solusek temple got better&quot; and &quot;your faction with Shadowmen got worse&quot;. We know verant likes to hide numbers from players, and this is one of those cases. When you kill the shadowman, your number for solusek temple faction gets an increase, like +50(random number) and your faction with shadowmen gets a decrease -50.<br>
<br>
Ok, well for your faction problem. You got your faction with Truespirit up to Warmly. It is still up there. They simply changed the faction that Caimen uses. He is no longer on the &quot;Truespirit&quot; faction. Now, he could be on one of the Erudin factions, it will be very difficult to figure out what faction applies to him. I am pretty sure that its not &quot;Crushbone Orcs&quot;, lol. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=76.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=76.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=76.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=76.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=76.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=76.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=76.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.